name: Candy fails to enter to enter a mandatory field

testSteps.description: Given Candy does not have a Frequent Flyer account
When Candy wants to register a new Frequent Flyer account

children.description: Candy goes to the login page
Candy opens the pages.home page
Candy clicks on Register button

testSteps.description:
Then the following information should be mandatory to register:
| Field | Error Message If Missing |
| email | Please enter your email |
| password | Please enter your password |
| firstName | Please enter your first name |
| lastName | Please enter your last name |
| address | Please enter your address |
| country | Please enter a valid country |

children.description: Candy checks each entry in the collection:
For item {Field=email, Error Message If Missing=Please enter your email}
Candy registers for a new Frequent Flyer account with email
Candy goes to the registration page
Candy opens the pages.registration page
Candy enters '' into Email field
Candy enters 'cand1' into Password field
Candy enters 'Candy' into First name field
Candy enters 'Traveller' into Last name field
Candy enters '10 Partridge Street, Dandenong' into Address field
Candy enters 'Australia' then hits [TAB] into Country field
Candy selects  'Mrs' from Title dropdown
Candy clicks on Title dropdown
Candy clicks on option
Candy clicks on Seat preference
Candy clicks on Terms and conditions
Candy clicks on Register button
Candy should see Error messages with text values that contains: <[Please enter your email]>
